snippet.title: Charles the Bee - Steam Next Fest: October 2023 Demo
snippet.description:
Charles has always dreamed of one day becoming a master dancer. The only thing in his path? The cost! Charles must harvest pollen until he has defeated the biggest and baddest dancers around in the world. Can he be the very best? That no one ever was? Its up to you!

The full version will have mod support for custom music, artwork and note charts, complete with a tool that can help you make the note charts as well.

Charles the Bee (C) Blue Pin Studio
Coming to Steam in November 2023

#steam #steamgames #steamgame #steamnextfest #steamnextfestoctober2023 #charliethebee
